00:59:12,040 --> 00:59:16,470
You are truly a disgrace to Cheong Ah Arts.

713
00:59:25,720 --> 00:59:27,520
What is this, huh?

714
00:59:28,330 --> 00:59:30,960
My Je Ni, on the performance test

715
00:59:30,960 --> 00:59:33,780
she placed third. Third place.

716
00:59:37,020 --> 00:59:40,010
My Min Hyeok is fourth.

717
00:59:40,010 --> 00:59:43,050
If he's fourth place, then he'll have no problems getting into Seoul National University of Music, right?

718
00:59:43,050 --> 00:59:48,060
Of course.  No one in the top five fails admission to a SKY Music School.  ( SKY: Seoul National U, Korea U, and  Yonsei U) 

719
00:59:48,060 --> 00:59:51,060
Did Teacher Cheon really show her ability?

720
00:59:51,060 --> 00:59:53,620
I've definitely decided the path I will follow.

721
00:59:53,620 --> 00:59:57,770
Until my Je Ni gets into Seoul National University of Music, unconditionally, to Teacher Cheon,

722
00:59:57,770 --> 00:59:58,970
I'll be loyal.

723
00:59:58,970 --> 01:00:04,070
Me too! It's not like she had an affair with my husband. I'll just close my eyes this once and forget it.

724
01:00:04,070 --> 01:00:05,560
Loyalty!

725
01:00:05,560 --> 01:00:06,990
Loyalty!

726
01:00:06,990 --> 01:00:08,900
Director.

727
01:00:09,690 --> 01:00:14,410
Ha Eun Byeol earned first place on the practical test by overwhelmingly better skills.

728
01:00:19,510 --> 01:00:23,390
I gave special consideration to the children you mentioned.

729
01:00:23,390 --> 01:00:25,510
Well done.

730
01:00:26,490 --> 01:00:27,590
What about Bae Ro Na?

731
01:00:27,590 --> 01:00:31,780
Bae Rona placed last.

732
01:00:33,110 --> 01:00:39,490
- Teacher Ma, the kids are looking so you don't have to go that far. 
- No.

733
01:00:39,490 --> 01:00:41,860
I didn't give her the worst grades intentionally.

734
01:00:41,860 --> 01:00:45,560
I don't know what she ate wrong, but she sang out of tune.

735
01:00:45,560 --> 01:00:46,660
Out of tune?

736
01:00:46,660 --> 01:00:49,620
I don't know why the child who worked like she was possessed by a devil for a test

737
01:00:49,620 --> 01:00:53,740
made such a mistake.

738
01:00:53,800 --> 01:00:58,900
All right.  I appreciate her failing on her own.

739
01:01:00,820 --> 01:01:02,600
Bae Ro Na.

740
01:01:03,440 --> 01:01:07,820
- I heard. You received the worst grades? 
 - Yes.

741
01:01:07,820 --> 01:01:10,400
I have no interest in what happened with you.

742
01:01:10,400 --> 01:01:13,620
But I can't forgive you for not preparing for the exams and ruining the learning environment.

743
01:01:13,620 --> 01:01:17,670
It could have a bad influence on the other kids.

