01:01:21,220 --> 01:01:23,660
  Dropout Letter    

745
01:01:23,660 --> 01:01:27,590
That's why I'm going to dropout of this school.

746
01:01:31,840 --> 01:01:33,460
What?

747
01:01:33,460 --> 01:01:36,400
You were right.

748
01:01:36,400 --> 01:01:41,580
Cheong Ah Arts School never suited someone like me from the start.

749
01:01:42,410 --> 01:01:45,030
I'll get lost now.

750
01:01:49,080 --> 01:01:52,490
Did you discuss this with your mom?

